This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on learning representations for rare words. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a method for predicting embeddings using a neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses auxiliary data to improve the embeddings, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method proposed in the paper involves training a network end-to-end, which is a technique used in neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the method on tasks such as reading comprehension and language modeling, which are common in computer vision (cs.CV).
